Download links:
VirtualBox: https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
Windows 10: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/evalcenter/download-windows-10-enterprise
SQL Server: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/sql-server/sql-server-downloads
SSMS: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/ssms/install/install

ODBC Driver installation:
Linux Terminal:
sudo apt install curl gnupg
curl https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc | sudo apt-key add -
sudo curl -o /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mssql-release.list https://packages.microsoft.com/config/debian/12/prod.list
sudo apt update
sudo ACCEPT_EULA=Y apt install msodbcsql18 unixodbc-dev

Python libraries required: pyodbc
Linux terminal:
apt install python3-pyodbc
